2) BASE STAT GAIN PER LEVEL (SIMPLE MODEL)
------------------------------------------
- E to A ranks:   +1 PHY (STR, AGI, VIT) and +2 INT per level
- S to Mythic-2:  +3 PHY and +5 INT per level
- Demi to Divine: +5 PHY and +10 INT per level

Notes:
- PHY = physical stats (STR, AGI, VIT)


3) RANK ATTRIBUTE GAIN TABLE (PER LEVEL)
----------------------------------------
| Rank                  | Attribute Gain Per Level | Typical Examples |
|-----------------------|--------------------------|------------------|
| E                     | +2                       | Regular humans; basic trainees |
| D                     | +3                       | Trained/elite humans; soldiers; knights; minor awakened |
| C                     | +4                       | Magic-capable mortals; low-tier adventurers; basic monster elites |
| B                     | +5                       | Beastkin; lesser vampires; high goblins; medium orcs; solid mid-tier players |
| A                     | +7                       | True vampires; high elves; dragonoid warriors; strong veteran players; elite commanders |
| S (Pinnacle)          | +10                      | National champions; named gate bosses; clan heads |
| SS-1 (Ascendant)      | +12                      | Refined S-rank veterans; lesser vampire lords; draconic lieutenants; demon captains |
| SS-2 (Sovereign)      | +14                      | Regional warlords; major vampire lords; dragon generals; demon dukes; city-destroyer threats |
| SS-3 (Transcendent)   | +16                      | Top vampire lords; draconic champions; demonic warlords; heroic legends nearing apotheosis |
| Mythic-1 (Legendary)  | +18                      | Archfey nobles; ancient dragon kings; high demon princes; region/world-class threats |
| Mythic-2 (Origin)     | +20                      | Realm guardians; proto-god champions; named calamities; Tower-chosen monsters |
| Demi (Demigod Class)  | +25                      | Primordial dragons; great demon kings; nascent god-rulers whose presence warps continents |
| Divine (God Tier)     | +30                      | True godborns; full divine hybrids; avatars; gods in mortal form |

Natural Limit (setting note):
- Most civilizations peak at B–A in a normal world.
- S and above are extremely rare; Mythic/Demi/Divine belong to legend/calamity/divinity.


